profile:
{"first_name": "Jeremy", "last_name": "Robison", "full_name": "Jeremy Robison", "headline": "President at Tetra Capital", "title": "President", "picture": {"source": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5603AQFZ3p9waFU73w/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/B56ZaL9YmpGUAw-/0/1746104847100?e=1779321600&v=beta&t=YWkUncTYGkHPmTKxjpADcJYXnqXq8340lGTS22zniUs"}, "background": null, "birth_date": "1600-10-26", "summary": "Since 1986 Tetra has provided its services to companies of all sizes and types. Our clients include many Fortune 500 companies, as well as smaller private enterprises. Despite the diversity of the companies we help, and the wide range of services we provide, there is one constant across every transaction—our unmatched customer service.

Whether you are in health care, information technology, banking, telecommunications, manufacturing, or any other industry, our experience means that we know best how to meet your needs. We set expectations up front so there are fewer surprises, providing our clients with a higher level of overall satisfaction.

Specialties: Equipment leasing and financing"}

{"first_name": "Thomas", "last_name": "L.", "full_name": "Thomas L.", "headline": "Chief Operating Officer at Factoring Express LLC", "title": "Chief Operating Officer", "picture": {"source": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E03AQG2xSm05AfVVQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0/1730214486203?e=1778716800&v=beta&t=5_MxheS8ECq3_R2Pb7jAZg8Yi6B0GNOhjxnleGyYzBQ"}, "background": {"source": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D5616AQF8QZVnMY4nhg/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/profile-displaybackgroundimage-shrink_350_1400/0/1730124808849?e=1778716800&v=beta&t=m6WkfXbSi7mBQQtJaVvMcoPPk4awPLXz8__umsQ23LI"}, "birth_date": "1600-09-10", "summary": "Thomas Longo is a highly accomplished executive with over 30 years of experience in the factoring and purchase order financing segments, Thomas has directed the growth of a factoring company by demonstrating his passion for business development, creating factoring policies, devising underwriting strategies, and forming new marketing campaigns. He has successfully driven highly profitable B2B revenue with mid-market enterprises and, as Chief Operating Officer of Factoring Express LLC, takes pride in using his knowledge and creativity to structure deals in such a way that enables the company to fund businesses others would turn away.  He's streamlined operating functions, re-written contracts and prospect onboarding material, focused on inner-company process improvements, and aided in the company's growth to become one of the top medical factoring companies in the Country. 

Prior to Factoring Express, Thomas served as Senior Vice President at Paragon Financial Group, Inc beginning back in 1998, where he created and launched the first international factoring advance entitled Documents in Possession, now known as Cash Against Documents. Thomas’s expertise and insights have been recognized in the factoring industry, and his article on the creation of Documents in Possession financing, has been featured in the American Cash Flow Journal. 

Thomas is married and resides in Fort Lauderdale, Florida."}

